He ticks so many hipster boxes at once. A beard and a flat cap, over which he's wearing huge headphones. Knowingly ironic unfashionable glasses too. I bet they don't even have a prescription. Shorts. Trainers with massive tongues, sticking half way up his shins. Unconventional, yet still a uniform to identify him as a certain type of person, a member of a particular group.

