A group of people who express their identities by trying to look like 1960s Yorkshiremen. Weekdays working down t' mill, weekends working the decks at an eclectic bar in Hoxton? Is that what we're supposed to think? Maybe this guy doesn't know what day of the week it is, so he's hedging his bets.
> interact person28
He looks like some sort of academic. Quite poor dress sense —  and if I can spot that, it must be really poor dress sense. He's reading some kind of scientific paper, and chuckling to himself.

This is Old Street.
I could get off here. Or wait.
